Home features an open concept with large great room that leads into dining room, a additional living room, beautiful kitchen w/ stainless steel appliances and breakfast bar. Great sized bedrooms, big laundry room/mudroom with 2 car attached garage. Walk up attic, concrete patio. AC 2019,Furnace 2023, new updated electrical panel in 2022.
